{"thi-ap11:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap11:0.2":"Ekuposathikavagga ","thi-ap11:0.3":"1 Ekuposathikatheriapadana ","thi-ap11:1.1":"“Nagare bandhumatiya, ","thi-ap11:1.2":"bandhuma nama khattiyo; ","thi-ap11:1.3":"Divase punnamaya so, ","thi-ap11:1.4":"upavasi uposatham. ","thi-ap11:2.1":"Aham tena samayena, ","thi-ap11:2.2":"kumbhadasi aham tahim; ","thi-ap11:2.3":"Disva sarajakam senam, ","thi-ap11:2.4":"evaham cintayim tada. ","thi-ap11:3.1":"‘Rajapi rajjam chaddetva, ","thi-ap11:3.2":"upavasi uposatham; ","thi-ap11:3.3":"Saphalam nuna tam kammam, ","thi-ap11:3.4":"janakayo pamodito’. ","thi-ap11:4.1":"Yoniso paccavekkhitva, ","thi-ap11:4.2":"duggaccanca daliddatam; ","thi-ap11:4.3":"Manasam sampahamsitva, ","thi-ap11:4.4":"upavasim uposatham. ","thi-ap11:5.1":"Aham uposatham katva, ","thi-ap11:5.2":"sammasambuddhasasane; ","thi-ap11:5.3":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap11:5.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap11:6.1":"Tattha me sukatam byamham, ","thi-ap11:6.2":"ubbhayojanamuggatam; ","thi-ap11:6.3":"Kutagaravarupetam, ","thi-ap11:6.4":"mahasanasubhusitam. ","thi-ap11:7.1":"Acchara satasahassa, ","thi-ap11:7.2":"upatitthanti mam sada; ","thi-ap11:7.3":"Anne deve atikkamma, ","thi-ap11:7.4":"atirocami sabbada. ","thi-ap11:8.1":"Catusatthi devarajunam, ","thi-ap11:8.2":"mahesittamakarayim; ","thi-ap11:8.3":"Tesatthi cakkavattinam, ","thi-ap11:8.4":"mahesittamakarayim. ","thi-ap11:9.1":"Suvannavanna hutvana, ","thi-ap11:9.2":"bhavesu samsaramaham; ","thi-ap11:9.3":"Sabbattha pavara homi, ","thi-ap11:9.4":"uposathassidam phalam. ","thi-ap11:10.1":"Hatthiyanam assayanam, ","thi-ap11:10.2":"rathayananca sivikam; ","thi-ap11:10.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","thi-ap11:10.4":"uposathassidam phalam. ","thi-ap11:11.1":"Sonnamayam rupimayam, ","thi-ap11:11.2":"athopi phalikamayam; ","thi-ap11:11.3":"Lohitangamayanceva, ","thi-ap11:11.4":"sabbam patilabhamaham. ","thi-ap11:12.1":"Koseyyakambaliyani, ","thi-ap11:12.2":"khomakappasikani ca; ","thi-ap11:12.3":"Mahagghani ca vatthani, ","thi-ap11:12.4":"sabbam patilabhamaham. ","thi-ap11:13.1":"Annam panam khadaniyam, ","thi-ap11:13.2":"vatthasenasanani ca; ","thi-ap11:13.3":"Sabbametam patilabhe, ","thi-ap11:13.4":"uposathassidam phalam. ","thi-ap11:14.1":"Varagandhanca malanca, ","thi-ap11:14.2":"cunnakanca vilepanam; ","thi-ap11:14.3":"Sabbametam patilabhe, ","thi-ap11:14.4":"uposathassidam phalam. ","thi-ap11:15.1":"Kutagaranca pasadam, ","thi-ap11:15.2":"mandapam hammiyam guham; ","thi-ap11:15.3":"Sabbametam patilabhe, ","thi-ap11:15.4":"uposathassidam phalam. ","thi-ap11:16.1":"Jatiya sattavassaham, ","thi-ap11:16.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","thi-ap11:16.3":"Addhamase asampatte, ","thi-ap11:16.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","thi-ap11:17.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap11:17.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","thi-ap11:17.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","thi-ap11:17.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thi-ap11:18.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","thi-ap11:18.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","thi-ap11:18.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","thi-ap11:18.4":"uposathassidam phalam. ","thi-ap11:19.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap11:19.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap11:19.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap11:20.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap11:20.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap11:20.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap11:21.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap11:21.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap11:21.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap11:22.1":"Ittham sudam ekuposathika bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap11:23.1":"Ekuposathikatheriyapadanam pathamam. "}